#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Collaboration is at the heart of Graasp Library, where educators and professionals come together to share, co-create, and learn. By sharing Open Educational Resources (OER), educators have access and contribute to a growing library of collective knowledge."
msgstr "La colaboración es fundamental en la Biblioteca Graasp, donde educadores y profesionales se reúnen para compartir, cocrear y aprender. Al compartir Recursos Educativos Abiertos (REA), los educadores acceden y contribuyen a una creciente biblioteca de conocimiento colectivo."

